article.description: — Kobe Julien had 17 points as Louisiana-Lafayette beat Troy 69-59 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Julien carries Louisiana-Lafayette over Troy 69-59
article.story: LAFAYETTE, La. -- — Kobe Julien had 17 points as Louisiana-Lafayette beat Troy 69-59 on Saturday night. Trajan Wesley had 12 points for Louisiana-Lafayette (9-8, 4-3 Sun Belt Conference). Kentrell Garnett added 11 points. Dou Gueye had 10 points and seven rebounds. Theo Akwuba had 4 points, nine rebounds, and five blocks. Efe Odigie had 14 points and nine rebounds for the Trojans (13-6, 4-2). Khalyl Waters added 11 points. Zay Williams had eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
